column6: bOdfx 72 Piece Complete Ear Stretching Kit. 14g-00g. Tapers, Tunnels & Plugs
column14:
This is a great started kit for ear stretching, my only real issue with this is that they are the regular tapers. Using the flat backed tapers became a bit difficult as I got to the bigger sizes so I had to but the concave tapers for those sizes. Also I would have liked to have a 9mm taper and jewelry set, but I understand they aren't very common it is more of a personal preference.

The tapers are great and work well, I'm not sure about the larger sizes because I didn't use them but they look to me like they are too short for the size of the stretch, potentially making it more painful and risking damage.

I love the stainless tunnels and I wear them all the time, they look great and are very comfortable.
I have only worn the acrylic plugs a handful of time but they were comfortable and looked nice, although I don't feel like I could wear them to bed in fear that the o rings could come off too easily.

column14:

It reflects the light nicely. It actually makes my real engagement ring look dingy and dirty next to it. I also really love the band on this ring. My normal ring size is 10 for my wedding finger, but I thought a 9 would be okay since I am not actually wearing it on that finger. It fits perfectly!

One of my friends did not believe me that she could buy it on Amazon for less than $12 (at the current price). I had to pull up Amazon and show her. I have been wearing this a lot and washing my hands often and so far I have had no issues. This seems to be a high quality ring and I can't wait to try out more Aiyaya jewelry.

column6:
Women's Stainless Steel Polished Heart Charm Bracelet - 7.5\"	Jewelry	2	30	34	N	Y	This bracelet is very pretty and well made	This bracelet is very pretty and well made.  It comes package eloquently in a nice velvet pouch and zip log bag and will really be appealing to the recipient.  It looks really nice and will hold up to many years of use so from that perspective, it is really a great charm bracelet!  It is described as fitting up to 8.5" and that is a completely misleading statement.  I purchased this item and received it and it was 8" in length.  With charms on the bracelet, it would not fit 8" either.  It would fit 7.5" as a snug bracelet or a 7" bracelet loosely.  I sent that bracelet back and received a replacement.  I thought maybe it was just a fluke and the next one would be accurately sized.  When I received the next bracelet, it was almost 8" in length.  The seller is counting the puffy heart dangling charm in the measurement and shouldn't.  The puffy heart is not part of the closure so it is very misleading.  I am measuring the actual bracelet - that secures around the wrist which is the most important measurement.  If you are buying this bracelet because you think it is a larger sized bracelet, you are going to be very disappointed in the fit. If you are looking for a nice item to fit a 7" wrist, this is your bracelet.  All they have to do is add a few more links to it to make it right.  I am rating this as a 2 because it is really not as described.  The seller states "Clasps on ANY link to adjust the length of the bracelet to your needs from 5 to 8.5 Inches" and it definitely does not.  The link part of the bracelet is almost 8".	2015-08-08

Kenneth Cole New York Faceted Bead Pendant Necklace, 21\" Jewelry 5 0 0 N Y GORGEOUS Got this on sale (finally)!! Glad I ordered the bracelet, necklace and earrings. I can't wait to wear the set. 2015-08-08 US 2370867 R1G02CK7RYXI70 B00R449PD8 306845614 HiRudolph 1 X The Legend of Zelda Skyward Sword Blue Heart Pierced Necklace Anime Costume Jewelry 4 1 1 N Y Neato! Here's a trick to it! Firstly, I'm quite satisfied that it came earlier than predicted! Fairly fast shipping for a product hailing from China. Now onto my little review.

At a glance, this big heart of blue captures the eye with its golden gleam and deeply shimmering azure stone of glass.
For my case, I came across a couple of minor issues; however they do not take away from the general wonderfulness of this product.

Within a few hours of first wearing it, the clasp's spring mechanism failed and broke, leaving me to remove it and connect the two rings together. Thankfully, the chain it comes with is quite easy to fit over the head, so the loss of the clasp was nothing mortifying.
Secondly, the frame itself seems a tad bent at the top of the heart, as if someone purposefully tried prying it off. The pretty glass gem inside mine in particular is certainly too small for the frame; although it matches in shape. However, I noticed that there is a small loop at the bottom of the heart, of which I used to wrap string through to keep the gem stable. Nonetheless, it still shakes around side to side, generating a fair amount of noise and concern over the glass. Glue in the edges of the frame should solve that issue, should any of you come across a similar case. I chose to be lazy and leave it be with the string --for now anyway.

Now back to the frame of the charm.
I've been wearing it steadily for a few days, perhaps even a week, and I've noticed signs of tarnishing in the 'gold' finish, most likely due to skin oil. Perhaps a frequent wipe-off or rinse will fix this, but I am unsure. I'm still experimenting upon the posting of this review.

Despite my little issues, I am satisfied with this product, especially for something with such a small price. Quality is fair, and only has small issues that are easily walked around. I'd say that these are a hit and miss with quality, and I happened to be in the middle ground with mine.
This necklace is overall a neat gift for Zelda fans, and I would recommend taking the gamble to grab yourself a neat heart container!

column13: Beautiful For Diamond Pendant, Strong For 24/7.
column14: 1) real white gold necklace 2) that looks great by itself or with a diamond pendant 3) that you can wear 24/7 without ever taking off. I bought this necklace because I needed a 20-inch real white gold necklace, to wear with a Halo Style Oval Cut 1.48 Ct Diamond Pendant, and never take off. I have literally worn this necklace 24/7 since I received it. I don't take my necklaces on and off. It is beautiful enough to look great with a drop-down halo style diamond pendant, and strong enough to wear 24/7 while sleeping, showering, everything. It was a little thinner than I thought it would be when I got it out of the box, but not too thin, looks-wise or durability-wise, to return it. I was happier with it when I put it on. It really catches the light, and sparkles all over, because of the cut. It looks great on, it holds the pendant great, it's strong, and it's real white gold. It's great to wear for everyday use, but it's also nice enough to wear for special occasions. I have worn it to special occasions, and it looked great in the photos. And, I have worn it 24/7 at home, and it still looks great in the mirror. I'm still happy with the necklace, and with the transaction. I would recommend this necklace.

column6: King Will GENTLEMAN Men 8mm Black Carbon Fiber Inlay Tungsten Carbide Ring 18K Rose Gold Plated Comfort Fit Wedding Band Engagement Ring
column14:
This was received at a discount or for free. It was received in hopes of my honest review. All thoughts are my own and no other's. This review is in the guidelines of the FTC.

This is my husband's new wedding band. He had lost so much weight that he could no longer keep his other one on and we needed to replace it. Well, when we first got married several years ago, we couldn't seem to get the rings right. They either broke, faded, or turned our fingers colors. We went through so many different rings, on both of us, that it became so irritating. Finally, I decided to change metals on our rings until I got it right to where we neither one would have our fingers changing colors, fading rings and the whole issue of what we were going through. We have came to a conclusion about our rings and other jewelry. No more gold as you can't tell anything about how it works or how well. Sterling Silver, Stainless Steel and now Tungsten. These are the three we agree on as they don't change your finger colors, brake or anything else. Tungsten is a high quality metal that I have to highly recommend. And of course, I highly recommend this ring! This is the ring my husband and I have finally settled on for our wedding bands.

column14: I'm using this for resale online. It will work for that. I had another black leatherette one I was using that I found in a 2nd hand store. It was cosmetically damaged but I made due with it for a while. When I started selling I didn't know how much I would use this. Then, when I realized it looked seriously crappy, and that I was going to use something like this a lot I bought a white leatherette one and black velvet one from this company. The bases of these from Nilecorp are not as thick and sturdy as the damaged one I was using. They are slightly cockeyed but really only slightly so. Because I am using this for photographs, I can easily account for that by centering my photo. However, if you are using this for display of your merchandise in a store or booth sales you might want to invest in sturdier models. ***Update*** I have now learned that if you can get a black leatherette you should. Every bit of dust, & micro-debri in the world shows up on this black velvet, especially in a photograph because of the lights! whaaa waaa

column6: Emitations Magnetic Stud Pearl Earrings for Women's
column14:
These are great!!! I ordered expecting them to not be that great but I LOVE them! The magnets are pretty strong. Yes, they will come off if you say, take a shirt off over your head or something like that. I don't see that as an issue, I just put them on last as I am dressing and take them off first. If you tend to pull your hair over your ear often throughout the day, or touch your face/ears you may have issues.
I have pierced ears that have closed up so I place the earring where I still have the opening (only my skin is closed up I still have the "hole") so the magnet has less to go through. My lobes also naturally have a "cupping" toward the back so it cradles the back magnet, if you have flat lobes that might impact how well they work.

Wow, usually I come up with a more clever title but this one just speaks for itself. No picture will do the depth of the color justice. I was given this product along with 3 other Oulaimu items for testing. They are all based off the same design concept, bright rich coloring with traditional designs.

The Jewelry box itself appears to hold a good amount of items, unfortunately I couldn't test that part as I don't have much Jewelry. What I can tell you is that it is made well for the price and matches other Oulaimu products. Great for a teenager who wants to add some pop into the room.

The product was provided in exchange for a review. There is little that I can find wrong with it hence the 4star rating. The price isn't clear at the time of writing this, however I see that it should be $18. At this price it is worth the purchase. The materials used, design and build quality all exceed that price point.

Thank you for reading!

column6: TRUSUPER Silver Evil Eye Hamsa White Blue CZ Pendant Necklace
column14:
When I saw this I thought is was beautiful but after I ordered I freaked out a little. I didn't' know what an evil eye was or what it stands for so I looked it up. After that I was very excited to get in this pendant. I'm so glad I didn't chicken out because it is even more stunning in person. The white CZ shine so bright they really do like diamonds around the beautiful blue center stone. It is a very pretty dressy pendant and would easily go with a wedding dress or a pair of jeans. The pendant is the perfect size so it will compliment any outfit but will not be overpowering.
The chain is very delicate and I almost gave the set to my daughter because the chain is a little too delicate. It's not short and it hangs just at my collar bone so I decided to keep this one for myself. The blue stone is enough to catch everyone's eye but combined with the shining CZ all around the eye there is no way anybody will not notice this around my neck. I can't wait to show it off everywhere I go.
I received this product complimentary in exchange for my honest opinion but the opinion expressed is all my own.

column13: that said this is an well made and comfortable though slightly heavy bracelet
column14:
I as a man used to wear lots of rings and a few necklaces, mostly the biker attitude stuff. so... no stranger to the issues with men and accessories. that said this is an well made and comfortable though slightly heavy bracelet. read up on tungsten carbide prior to ordering. This is the ultimate metal though it does have one flaw.(tendency to shatter, again, read up on it).
The color is an awesome grey/black almost deflective of light yet shiny at the same time.(again read up on it).
one caution, the size is set. you would have to have a jeweler to change the clasp or add links which in my opinion would ruin what it is.
Both the skin side and outside are smooth and polished (again read up on the characteristics of tungsten carbide)
bottom line, this is an awesome piece of jewelry, art and craftsmanship.

column6: Wizardry Jewelry Double Pack Silver Keychain And Bracelet Triangle Symbol
column13: Cute and fun set. Great for Harry Potter fans!
column14:
Now, keep in mind that this is fun, costume jewelry and great for any Harry Potter fan. I have a friend who loves Harry Potter and absolutely loved this set. The quality is okay, but it's still really cute and a great conversational piece. They're both made of a silver alloy metal and the bracelet has a black like cord. Both pieces are lightweight, easy to get on with both having clasps and I like that the bracelet is adjustable. Overall, I like the Harry Potter movies and all, but I wouldn't call myself a huge fan or anything. However, I have come to realize that there is a huge Potter fan base that would love this set. I don't know how long these will last, but they would still make a cute gift to give.

Disclosure: I was not financially compensated for this post nor was I required to write a positive review. The opinions are my own and based on my personal experience with the product. I received one of the product mentioned above for free for my unbiased and honest opinion and was not compensated in any other way.

column14:
Now you can even wear a kitty around your neck! This non-gaudy, decent sized cat pendant is very, very sweet not to mention sparkly! column6: Olen Cubic Zirconia Wedding Band Ring
column14:
Lots of cubic zirconia crystals in this sparkling ring! The large one in the middle of the ring is approximately 3/8" in diameter. (This is not a small stoned ring!) It is flat on top BUT has been cut into multiple facets underneath so still sparkles when you look at it. The main stone is set in place with four claws. The band is relatively thin being just 1/16" at the back.

Presented in a small cardboard box, this ring appears to be great value for the price. I wear a size 8 1/2 ring on my wedding finger. The ring I ordered was a size 8. (No bigger size available.) I could have squeezed it on but was afraid that I wouldn't be able to get it off again! SO I truly believe that the ring sizes quoted are accurate therefore please make sure you order the size you normally wear.

PLEASE remember that although designed as an engagement ring this is still what I would consider "fashion jewelry". It is platinum-plated copper. How long will the plating last? Who knows! At this price, however, you can afford to replace it regularly for the latest fashion! Product provided in exchange for an honest review. Thanks, Liz

column6: Olen Cubic Zirconia Wedding Band Ring
column14: The ring is stunningly beautiful. I won't say that the centre stone looks like a real diamond but it has a nice sparkle to it. The centre stone is a round cut set on with 4 prongs and is surrounded by a square base with smaller stoned studded on it. There are also some smaller stoned studed on the band (4 on either side of the center piece). I have been wearing the ring continuously for a whole day now, and washed dishes, showered, gave my daughter a bath, cooked and best thing about the ring is that none if the stones lost its shine neither did the band lose its colors. Sometimes wearing a costume metal ring tends to make my fingers green but this food not do that, the metal looks pretty solid and sturdy and food not bend when I pressed out between my fingers. Over ask it it's an impressive design and a nice ring to have, the only thing that I faced with the ring is the size, I wear 6.5 and as there was not fraction sizes available I ordered the next size 7, so I thought it would be slightly loose on my finger but I was surprised that the ring fitted exactly like my 6.5 sized ring, so if I would have been a size 7 it would have been a little tight on my fingers. But for now ask us good as the ring fits my fingers perfectly I have no worries, but I feel they run half a size small. **I received the product as a promotional offer in exchange of my unbiased review.

I was assuming it would weigh your finger down so my fiancé wore it to work the following day just to see and he came home that evening saying that it did not weigh down at all on his finger and he wanted to keep wearing it instead of saving for the wedding. This ring is very well
Made and strong. The design is simple yet classy. I love the color of the black it is matte which is great. My fiancé always said he did not want a shinny ring that would show scratches easily. column14:
This bangle bracelet is ABSOLUTELY GORGEOUS! Okay, so I will admit to being partial to blue stones but the way these are set and cut are very pretty. There is one large heart (3/8") in the center and then four more on each side graduated in size.

VERY important to note that this bangle is NOT going to fit everyone! It is actually quite small being only 2 5/16" across the widest part. With the way it is designed (no hinge) you have to be able to slip it over your wrist. I have only given it a 4 star rating because the chain attached with the wider link to make for easy coupling needs to be longer. It is physically impossible to do the clasp up on the wider ring even when off your wrist as the two cannot meet! This means that you have to use one of the smaller links so you most likely will need another person to help you. I did!

PLEASE remember that this is fashion jewelry. It is only white gold plated. The underneath part is solid though making for a sturdy bracelet. Would I recommend this to others? Yes! Product provided in exchange for an honest review. Thanks, Liz

column13: Shine shine and sparkle! Stunning necklace!!
column14: Wow! Shine shine and sparkle! This necklace is a stunner! The design is unique, and the Swarovski elements crystal is cut so well, it shimmers and sparkles like crazy! The chain was tangled when I got it out of the box, but it didn't take long to straighten out.  Just be careful, because part of the chain is wrapped to hold the pendant.  I love the double strand chain, it measures 16" with a 2" extender, so 20" total length.  The pendant (measured just the crystal part) has a 1" drop.  The crystal back is encased in metal, not spray painted silver like some cheaper brands.  The cut is amazing, you won't believe the sparkle on this necklace! It comes in a standard paper gift box, and mine included a free scarf gift.  I received it free in exchange for my honest review.

column6: 18k Gold and Rhodium Plated Sterling Silver Two Tone Diamond Hoop Earrings (1/10cttw, I-J Color, I2-I3 Clarity)
column13: Nice size and sparkle. Doesn't look cheap
column14:
These earrings come presented in a nice black box with a velvet type inlay. The box is actually a little on the large side for the earrings themselves but that doesn't detract from it.

The earrings themselves are 18k gold and rhodium plated. Rhodium being the new hot thing in jewelry at the moment. It is a very precious metal that can cost as much as 10x that of gold. It is the most reflective of precious metals and helps bring out the dazzling shine of precious stones. Nothing sets of diamonds better than Rhodium plating which is why a lot of jewelers are now using it. In this case it works.

The earrings are a woven figure of 8 type that are about average size, not as big as a lot of hoop earrings and don't hang too far down off the ear lobe. Inset into each band of the weave are tiny little diamonds. These are very small and I counted 5 diamonds on each earring interspersed with the rhodium in the shape of small diamonds.

These earrings do not look cheap or plasticky (something a lot of this cheap jewelry does) and looks as though they are something you would buy at a jewelers in the mall.

Overall a very nice and sparkling pair of earrings that my wife is extremely happy with.

column6: ã€Deal of the Dayã€‘SWAROVSKI ELEMENTS CRYSTALS HEART SHAPE BANGLE BRACELET FOR WOMEN GIRLS WHITE GOLD PLATED FASHION WEDDING BRIDAL JEWELRY
column14:
I really love Swarovski products. They are always so beautiful.
This Swarovski Elements Crystal Heart Shaped Bracelet is gorgeous!
It is made of White Gold Plated Alloy which should hold up really well without rusting like regular plated jewelry. And Alloy is so much easier to keep clean and shiny.

I rated it 4 stars only because It is a little on the small side, luckily I have smaller wrists so it fits but is still a little snug. If you have bigger wrists then it might not fit you. And it is very hard to put it on yourself.

I really love how the crystals sparkle when the sun hits them. It looks so beautiful and stunning. The hearts are different sizes. The middle one is bigger then it goes smaller and smaller which makes it a really beautiful design.

It came in a beautiful gift box with a cleaning cloth to keep your bracelet shiny.
This bracelet looks gorgeous no matter what I wear it with so it's very versatile.
This would make a great present for any woman in your life. And it would also make the best Bridesmaid gift.

column14:
This is probably the most "grown up" pair of earrings I've ever worn.

They are about 3/4s of inch in diameter, and in normal lighting, not very sparkly. The settings are very smooth and don't snag my hair.

These would be 4 stars, except that the flat wires are a bit on the thick side. They didn't work at all in the bottom set of holes in my ears. I had to move them up. They do latch securely but latching them can be a little tricky because of the amount of play in the wire hinge. I know some people prefer the thicker, sturdier wires so what's a flaw for me is a design feature for others.

I like the size and style, but don't think I'll wear them often because of the wires.

column6: JDZ Amulets Tibetan Buddhist 108 Beaded Bracelet Porcelain Prayer Beads Wrist Meditation Mala Bracelet
column14:
This string of earth tone beads makes a statement about you. You are spiritual. You are relaxed. You are one with the cosmos and creation. There is nothing more relaxing than to find a quiet spot, close your eyes, and let your fingers rub and walk along a string of polished beads. Yes, I know it sounds all "hippy-dippy" but in the average person's average day anymore - it's essential to take a few moments to let your mind empty of all the trials, tribulations and stress it's accumulated and then re-boot.

These lovely beads are the perfect tool for that purpose.They're made of polished porcelain and number 108 which is the traditional number for a mala. When used in meditation you can count off each mantra recited. The strand is closed with a traditional Chinese Knot - I'm sorry but I don't know the exact name of this now - maybe someone will comment and help out. The bottom line is that this is a lovey piece of traditional Buddhist culture that you'll value for its purpose and simplicity. (Complimentary product received for evaluation.)

column13: Review For Blue Topaz and Other Colors Available in this Pretty Little Pendant
column14:
At super low prices on Amazon's End of Season sale, I purchased this pendant in blue topaz, amethyst, citrine and peridot, with the garnet coming. I'd already ordered each of the colors in the matching earrings to put away in my gift stash for friends and family (see my other reviews); the pendants make very pretty sets with the earrings. Each pendant measures 3/4 inch long from the top of the bale by just over 1/2 inch wide, and they're nice. I will say the chain is far too thin and delicate to be useful for most gals. It should be replaced with a better chain, a thin leather or satin cord, or even a ribbon cord if you plan to get a lot of wear. The bale opening is about 4mm, so be sure a clasp isn't larger than that when replacing the chain. Being rhodium plated means the bright, white silver shouldn't tarnish. Each pendant appears to be well made. Here's a breakdown of each, color by color:

Blue Topaz -- a clear, crisp, icy blue as shown on the product page, it matches the earrings for color

Amethyst -- fully saturated, it isn't pale, but is also not dark; it's more of a grape jelly tone and also matches the earrings

Peridot -- the center stone is light and clear, not cloudy as the earrings were, but it's very pale

Citrine -- a bit darker than the earrings, it's still a pale yellow stone that's more of a cool tone than one normally sees in citrine

Garnet -- will edit to add the information when the pendant arrives, but if it's at all like the earrings, will be the most striking of the colors

Each pendant comes in a gift box, but in a plastic bag tucked into the gift box, so you'll want to remove it from the plastic bag and arrange it before giving as a gift. Again, I recommend replacing the chain. At the deeply discounted sale price, they're worth picking up. It's a nice, inexpensive piece for everyday wear... simple and understated... appropriate for nurses, school teachers, chefs, office workers, teens, moms, grandmas, etc.teens, moms, grandmas, etc.
